flowchart TB
    A[Start: User Submits Application] --> B{Application Validated?}
    B -->|Validate Application| C{Course Spaces Available?}
    B -->|Invalid| D[Reject Application]
    C -->|Yes| E[Assign to Nearest Available Teacher]
    C -->|No| F[Add to Waiting Buffer]
    F --> G{Buffer Full?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Remove Oldest Application]
    G -->|No| I[Queue Application]
    H --> I
    E --> J[Notify User of Course Placement]
    I --> K[Notify User of Waiting Status]
    D --> L[End Process]
    J --> L
    K --> L
